	(gr_text "B1 PCB outline v0.5 — full Polycase ML-34BF-PCB template\nEnvelope: 104.7 x 79.3 mm with 4x R.377 (9.6 mm) outer corners\n4 edge notches centered on each side (R.125 / 3.18 mm inside fillets)\nTop/bottom notches: 73.9 mm wide x 9.6 mm deep\nLeft/right notches: 46.6 mm wide x 9.6 mm deep\n8 mounting holes NPTH 3.18 mm: 4 outer @ 85 x 60.3 mm, 4 inner @ 50 x 28.6 mm\nGNSS antenna NOT on main PCB (separate carrier above/perpendicular)"
